SELECT
  id,
  argMax(name, time) AS name,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    0,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(ratio, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS change_requests_accepted_ratio,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    0,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(accepted_count, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS change_requests_accepted,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    0,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(declined_count, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS change_requests_declined

FROM
(
  SELECT
    toStartOfYear(created_at) AS time,
    org_id AS id, argMax(org_login, time) AS name,
    COUNT() AS count,
    countIf(pull_merged = 1) AS accepted_count,
    countIf(pull_merged = 0) AS declined_count,
    accepted_count/count AS ratio
  FROM gh_events
  WHERE type = 'PullRequestEvent' AND action = 'closed'  AND (org_id IN [1342004]) AND  created_at >= toDate('2015-1-1') AND created_at < dateAdd(month, 1, toDate('2016-12-1'))
  GROUP BY id, time
  
)
GROUP BY id
ORDER BY change_requests_accepted_ratio[-1] DESC
    LIMIT 3
